{
  "stem": "21626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had this big tag around my neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the leader of the transport who was in charge of the transport came to me and said, I had news that your foster parents can't come for you today.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you're coming with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was taken in a big car to a huge house somewhere near a park.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I presume it was Hyde Park.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never learned the man's name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was either a bishop or archbishop, even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tried later to find out who it could have been, but there were quite a few high dignitaries, dignitaries of the church involved in the rescue of children from occupied Europe.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, it could have been-- you know, there was Archbishop of Canterbury, Archbishop of-- I, I don't know, there were, there were just so many.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this one had twin daughters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were, to me, grown-up daughters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They must have been about 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was told that they had a, they had a Czech companion, which really thrilled me because I didn't know, didn't know a word of English except three phrases which my parents taught me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And anyway, when I got to this big house, which was on four floors, and they had a lift, and they had a, a, a butler and maids, you know, and a cook and everything, and I was taken to this very austere room with tapestries and very sort of sedate, old-fashioned colors, all reds and rusts.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it seemed very, very foreign to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This lady appeared and said, you know-- greeted me in Czech.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was so pleased.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was the companion of the, of those daughters of this bishop or whoever he was.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
